s month/day boundary related. The scan also reports mixed UTC/local date handling in `src/date.ts`, so billing should avoid local `getMonth()`, `getDate()`, etc. unless the business rule explicitly depends on the customer’s locale/timezone.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"turn.completed\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":29264,\"cached_input_tokens\":12160,\"output_tokens\":461,\"reasoning_output_tokens\":24}}\n",
