\\nexpect(invoice.periodStart).toBe(\\\"2026-03-01\\\");\\n```\\n\\nI would fix `src/billing.ts` first by removing repeated wall-clock reads, then audit the date helper for the UTC/local mix because that is the most likely source of off-by-one date behavior across machines.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"turn.completed\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":29264,\"cached_input_tokens\":12160,\"output_tokens\":533,\"reasoning_output_tokens\":74}}\n",
